page.title: 14A RESIDENT BOREHAM NORTH 1
page.content: Ann lives in a semi-detached 300 year old cottage in a rural area.She is 36 years old married with a son and daughter. Her height is 5ft. and her weight is 7 stone. Ann has spent a lot of time renovating her home,and now loves it because she has "Put so much of myself into it" Inspite of this Ann is looking forward to moving to South Wales shortly. Her hobbies include knitting, walking, sewing and reading, she particularly enjoys science fiction. A Day in the Life of Ann. Ann gets up at 7 oclock and prepares breakfast Musli or Weetabix, honey and toast. The children leave for school and Ann travels to Basildon Market,to help her mother in law run a wholefood stall. They sell beans, rice, dried fruit,sugar-free jams, honey and over 200 herbs and spices.
